/--
EOS Theorem 7 canonical finite-tail certificate form. Under the standard
sorted-rank assumptions, canonical finite VCG-tail equality, and terminal
nonnegative comparison total payments, Lean derives the ranked `B*`
VCG-equivalent local-envy-free, stable, and revenue-minimal conclusion.
