/--
The exact finite-`B*` local-optimality dynamic-game certificate exposes belief
consistency for the named finite-`B*` strategy.
-/
theorem paper_theorem8_bstar_ranked_threshold_dynamic_game_named_strategy_consistent_belief_of_local_optimality_extensional_outcome_certificate
    {Belief : Type*}
